text.section:
In this section, "political subdivision" includes a:
county;
municipal corporation;
bicounty or multicounty agency;
county board of education;
public authority; or
special taxing district.

This section does not apply to:
a vessel;
a military, fire, or law enforcement vehicle;
a farm-type tractor, other agricultural equipment used for agricultural purposes, or construction equipment used for agricultural purposes or earth moving;
earth-moving or construction equipment used for those purposes; or
a lawn mower, snowblower, garden or lawn tractor, or golf cart while being used for its designed purpose.
